Examen Pedro.
148.60.0.0/16

Se configura SSH
Configurar RIP para toda la red

Configuracion:

Routers: -------------------------------

=== ElCabrito =========================

ena
conf t
hostname ElCabrito

// Conexion MSw 1
int g0/2
ip add 148.60.64.65 255.255.255.240
no shut

standby version 2
standby 1 ip 148.60.64.68
standby 1 priority 150
standby 1 preempt

// Conexion Router LaVaca
int g0/1
ip add 148.60.64.81 255.255.255.252
no shut

// Conexion Router Cloud
int g0/0
ip add 148.60.64.65 255.255.255.252
no shut

